  m_text: "Goal: Make as many orders correct as possible before the time runs out.\nSteps
    to create Suri\n1) SuriBread -> Suri Maker\n2) Frozen Food  -> Fryer -> Suri
    Maker\n3) Rest of Ingrdients -> Suri Maker (return them to free your hand)\nSuri
    from Suri Maker -> Grill -> Bag -> Takeout\nAccept orders from register and put
    the order reciepts on the suri  when you are finished\nBe careful for some components
    you have a limited number (ordered on depleted) \nYou will be judged based on
    Accuracy and Speed"
